text:
Oh, hey. Good morning.
You're up early again today.

You too, Producer!
I thought I'd be the first today!
Haha, is this a competition now?

Hehe, you have work to do, Producer.
Thanks for everything!

It's really not that big of a deal...
Meguru and the others do much more.

A reward for your hard work!
There's a coffee maker in the cafeteria, right?

Wait, wait.
I can't have my idol doing that.

Come on, Producer...
You don't have to worry about that!

I just want to express my gratitude!
Right?

Thanks, Meguru.
I'll take you up on that.

Sure!!
I'll make you the best cup ever!
